faq.name: PQV
faq.description: PERSONAL QUALIFYING VOLUME (PQV): Qualifying Volume that is generated through a Brand Partner’s personal product purchases. It also includes volume from product purchases made directly from the Company by a Brand Partner’s retail and Preferred Customers.

faq.name: GQV
faq.description: GROUP QUALIFYING VOLUME (GQV): The total Qualifying Volume of a specific group of Brand Partners. Includes Brand Partners’ PQV (max. 2,000 PQV from personal purchases counted toward GQV).
